dict.string: Today is 35 days, which are five weeks, of the Omer.
Hoy es treinta y cinco días, que son cinco semanas del Omer.
Aujourd'hui est trente-cinq jours, qui sont cinq semaines du Omer
СЕГОДНЯ ТРИДЦАТЬ ПЯТЬ ДНЕЙ - ЧТО СОСТАВЛЯЕТ ПЯТЬ НЕДЕЛЬ - ОМЕРА.
הַיּוֹם חֲמִשָּׁה וּשְׁלֹשִׁים יוֹם שֶׁהֵם חֲמִשָּׁה שָׁבוּעוֹת לָעֽוֹמֶר

Walking humbly is walking tall. Dignity is the essence of humility and modesty. The splendor of humility is majestic and aristocratic. Humility that suppresses the human spirit and denies individual sovereignty is not humility at all.
Teach someone how humility and modesty enhance human dignity.
Does my humility make me feel dignified?
Do I feel alive and vibrant?
